h3 {Dolmatov} Qb6 14. Qd2) 13... Rc8 (13... Qb6 $5) (13... Qb6 $5 {Ftacnik})
14. h3 Qb6 {Black seems to obtain a comfortable position after the opening.
White's g3 knight is quite passive; his king is not safe enough both in the
centre and  on the Q-side. However, Black's king is in danger too.} (14... d5 {
Boensch} 15. e5 (15. exd5 Nxd5 16. Nxd5 Bxd5 $10) 15... Nh7 $1 $15) 15. Qd2 (
15. Qc1 Nd4 16. Bd3 (16. Be3 $2 {Ftacnik} Nxc2+ 17. Qxc2 Qxe3 $17)) 15... Bg7 (
