17. a3 (17. Be3 $10 {Boensch}) 17... Na5 $40) 16. Bxd6 Nxg4 {The complication
started with this move prove rather favourable for White. Therefore 16...Nd4
17.Ba3 Rd8 deserved serious attention.} (16... Nd4 {Dolmatov} 17. e5 $5 (17.
Ba3 Rd8 18. Bd3 $14) 17... Qxb2 18. exf6 (18. Qxd4 {Ftacnik} Qxa1+ 19. Kd2
