coordinate his exposed pieces.} (18. a4 Bxc3 19. Rb1 Bc6 $15) 18... O-O (18...
Bb6 $6 19. c4 $1 $16) 19. c4 (19. a4 g6 20. Qe5 Bc7 21. Qf6 Bc4 $13) 19... Rxc4
20. a4 Rb4 $1 {
Little artistic, but probably best. Black can not afford to lose material.} (
