Be6 15. Bd3 f5 16. Bc2 (16. O-O Ra7 17. Qh5 e4 18. Bc2 Qe8 19. Qxe8 Rxe8 20. f3
exf3 21. Rxf3 Ne5 22. Rg3 Rf7 23. Nf4 Nc4 24. Nxe6 $14 {
Ivanchuk,V-Kramnik,V/London PCA (3)/1994/0.5 (52)}) (16. Qh5 Qd7 (16... Ne7 17.
Nxe7+ Qxe7 18. Nxf5 Qf6 {Vogt,L-Bukacek,E/Lenk op (8)/1991/1-0 (18)} 19. Ne7+
$1 Qxe7 20. Bxh7+ (20. Qxh7+ Kf7 21. Bg6+ Kf6 22. Qh4+ Kxg6 23. Qxe7 $18) 20...
Kh8 21. Bf5+ $1 Kg8 22. Qh7+ Kf7 23. Qg6+ Kg8 24. Bxe6+ $18) (16... e4 17. Bc2
Ne7 18. Bb3 Nxd5 19. Nxd5 a5 20. Nf4 Bxb3 21. axb3 Qe7 22. O-O b4 $5 23. cxb4
Qe5 24. Qg5 {Adams,M-Beliavsky,A/Debrecen/1992/0.5 (54)}) 17. g4 e4 18. Bc2
Rae8 19. O-O-O Ne5 20. gxf5 Bxf5 21. Nb6 Bg4 22. Nxd7 Bxh5 23. Nxf8 Bxd1 24.
Nxd1 {Vogt,L-Klundt,K/Bad Woerishofen op (08)/1992/0-1 (42)}) 16... Bh6 {
Black have prepared an agressive plan in order to avoid positional problems
with pawn chain d6-e5-f5.} (16... Ne7 17. Bb3 (17. O-O Ng6 18. f3 Bh6 19. Re1
Ra7 20. b4 Rg7 21. Kh1 Nh4 22. Re2 f4 23. Nf1 {
Larduet,C-Ochoa De Echaguen,F/Capablanca mem-C (12)/1992/0-1 (23)}) 17... Kh8
18. Nxe7 Qxe7 19. Qh5 h6 20. O-O f4 21. Nd5 Bxd5 22. Bxd5 Rab8 {
Jansson,A-Kytoniemi,J/Osterskan op/1994/0.5 (23)}) 17. O-O Ra7 (17... f4 18.
Qh5 Qg5 (18... fxe3 $2 19. Qxh6 exf2+ 20. Rxf2 Rxf2 21. Bxh7+ Kf7 22. Bg6+ Kg8
23. Qh7+ Kf8 24. Qh8+ Bg8 25. Qh6#) 19. Qxg5+ Bxg5 20. Nc7 fxe3 21. Nxe6 exf2+
22. Rxf2 Be3 23. Nxf8 Rxf8 24. Raf1 $14) 18. f4 Qh4 (18... Raf7) 19. g3 Rg7 $2
{This backfires badly. Black should have noticed, that in case should his
attack fail center was left dangerously unprotected.} (19... Qh3 20. a4 $14 (
20. Nc7 Rxc7 21. Qxd6 Re7 22. Nd5 Bxd5 23. Qxd5+ Rff7 24. Qxc6 exf4 $40) (20.
Ng2 Nd4 21. cxd4 Bxd5 $132)) 20. Nc7 $1 {Illescas was reportedly shocked by
this surprising jump, since he must have had the position on the board at
home!} exf4 (20... Rxg3+ 21. hxg3 Qxg3+ 22. Ng2 Bc4 23. Qf3 $18) 21. Ng2 Qh3 (
21... Qe7 22. Nxe6 Qxe6 23. Bb3 $18) 22. Rxf4 $1 {Few tactical blows have
decided the issue before black had got any chance to fire a single shot.} (22.
Nxe6 fxg3 23. hxg3 Be3+ $1 24. Rf2 (24. Nxe3 Qxg3+ $19) 24... Bxf2+ 25. Kf1
Bxg3 $19) 22... Bxf4 (22... Rxc7 23. Rh4 Qxh4 24. Nxh4 $16) 23. Nxf4 Rxg3+ 24.
Kh1 $1 (24. hxg3 Qxg3+ 25. Ng2 Ne5 $1 26. Nxe6 Nf3+ 27. Qxf3 Qxf3 28. Nxf8 Qe2
29. Bxf5 Kxf8 30. Rf1 Qxb2 31. Bc8+ Kg7 $13) 24... Qh6 (24... Qh4 25. Ncxe6 $18
) (24... Qg4 25. Ncxe6 $18) 25. Qxd6 (25. Qxd6 Nd8 26. Nfxe6 $18) (25. Ncxe6
$18) 1-0

