es the open c and d-files, to activate his R Black will have to shed material.}
Rac8 (27... Rad8 28. Rxd8 Rxd8 29. Rc5 $10) 28. Rxc8 Rxc8 29. Rd5 Rc1+ (29...
Rf8 30. Kf1 Kg7 31. Ke2 Kf6 32. Ke3 $44 {With a passive R Black would have no
