22. Qxg5 Qxg5 23. Rxg5 cxd4 $36 {
><Bh5,Dunnington,A-Lerner,K/Cappelle la Grande op/1996/}) (6... c6 7. O-O-O (7.
f4 $142 $13) 7... e5 8. Nf3 Be7 9. Kb1 Nd7 10. Ne2 Nf8 11. Qa5 Ng6 12. Ng3 Bd8
13. Qc3 O-O 14. d5 cxd5 15. Rxd5 Bb6 16. Qe1 Bg4 17. Rd2 Nf4 18. Ng1 Rac8 19.
f3 Be6 20. N1e2 Rc6 $15 {Summerscale,A-Knezevic,B/Cannes op/1996/}) 7. O-O-O
