Bxd8 52. f8=Q#) 51. Qxe5+ Bf6 52. Qxf6+ Qxf6 53. gxf6 h5 (53... h6 54. Kf3 Kh7
55. Kf4 Kh8 56. Ke5 Kh7 57. Ke6 Rb8 58. Bb5 Rf8 59. Ke7 $16) 54. Kf3 Kh7 55.
Kf4 Kh6 56. Ke5 g5 57. Ke6 Rb8 58. Bb5 Rh8 (58... Kg6 {Dolmatov} 59. Be8 Rb6+
60. Ke5 Rxf6 61. f8=Q+ $18) 59. Ke7 Kg6 60. Bd3+ 1-0

