30. Bd3 Bxd3 31. Rxd3 Bf2 32. Rd7 {White has some winning chances}) (27... Bh4
{Dolmatov} 28. Rg1 Rc5 29. f4 Be4 30. Bd3 Bxd3 31. cxd3 Kh7 $15) 28. Rh1 Bg3
29. Rh5 {and White is winning}) (27. Rh1 {Ftacnik} Bh4) 27... Bc6 28. Rxa7 Rd8
