35. Bf1 Bxf2+ $19) (34. h3 Bb6 {and black gets  intiative.}) 34... Qxf3 35.
Qxd8 Bxf2+ 36. Nxf2 Qxc6 37. Qg5+ Kf8 38. Qxe5 $11) 34. Qb4 Nb6 (34... a5 $5)
35. Qe7 (35. Rc7 Bb2 36. Rxa7 $140 $2 Rd1+ 37. Bf1 Nd5 $19) 35... Bb2 $2 (35...
Rd7 36. Qh4 (36. Qb4 $11) 36... Nd5 37. Nd6 Bxf2+ $1 (37... Ne7 38. Ne8+ Kf8
39. Be4 $16) 38. Kxf2 Rxd6 39. Rxd6 Qc2+ 40. Ke1 Qc1+ 41. Ke2 Qc2+ $11) 36. h4
$2 (36. Nc5 $1 Rd1+ 37. Bf1 Kh8 (37... Kh6 38. Nxe6 $1 $18) 38. Qxa7 Qb1 39.
