41. Qc3 $14) 38. Qc2 Nd5 $11) 37. Kh2 Nd5 38. Qe8 (38. Qxa7 Nf6 (38... Bd4 39.
Qb8 $18) 39. Nxf6 Qxf6 40. Rc8 Rd8 (40... Bd4 41. Qa8) 41. Rc2 Bd4 42. Qa5 {
with big advantage.}) 38... Nf6 39. Nxf6 $8 Qxf6 40. Rc8 Kh6 41. Qf8+ Qg7 42.
Qc5 Qg6 (42... Bd4 43. Qc2 Qg4 44. Rf8 (44. Rh8 e4) 44... Qg7 45. Qc8 (45. Re8
Qg4 46. Re7 Kg7) 45... Bxf2 (45... f6 46. Qe8 $18 (46. Rg8 Qf7)) 46. Rg8 Bxg3+
47. Kh3 $18) 43. Bf3 (43. Qe3+ $1 Kg7 44. Qxa7 Qf6 45. Qc5 {
and white wins easily.}) 43... Rd7 44. g4 f6 45. Qf8+ (45. Bc6 $1 Rf7 $8 46.
Be8 Qxg4 47. Qe3+ (47. Bxf7 Qxh4+ 48. Kg2 Qg4+ $11) 47... Kg7 48. Bxf7 Qxh4+
49. Kg2 Bd4 50. Qg3+ Qxg3+ 51. Kxg3 Kxf7 52. Rc7+ Kg6 53. b4 {
and white must win.}) 45... Qg7 46. Qe8 $2 (46. Qc5 Bd4 (46... Qg6 47. Bc6 {
see 45 Bc6}) 47. Qc1+ Kg6 48. Bc6 Re7 49. Be8+ $18) 46... Qf7 47. Qh8 e4 $1 {
Very strong, black's idea to  dictract white's bishop from h5 field.} (47...
Qg7 $4 48. Rg8 $3 $18) 48. Bxe4 (48. Be2 Rd2) 48... Qg7 49. Qxg7+ Kxg7 $11 50.
Rc6 Bxa3 51. Rxe6 Re7 52. Ra6 Bc5 53. f3 Bb6 54. Ra2 Bc7+ 55. Kh3 Bf4 56. Ra5
h6 57. Rf5 Bd2 58. Kg2 Re5 1/2-1/2

