gives Black good compensation with a draw whenever he wants.} (13. Qc6 $6 O-O {
/\Ne5,Rb6,><K,Q})) 12... Rb8 $8 13. Qxa6 Nh5 (13... Rxb2 $5 14. Nb5 (14. Qxd6
