Rb6 $143 14. Qe2 Nh5 15. Bc1 $5 {
and the misplaced Rb6 just gives White a tempo to advance his passed pawn.})
14. Bc1 (14. Bxd6 $2 Rb6 $19) (14. Qxd6 $2 Nxf4 15. Qxf4 Rxb2 $40) 14... O-O
15. Be2 (15. Qxd6 $4 Rb6) ({
