Qe5 $19) 31... Ra8 32. Bf1 $3 $18 {/\Rd6} (32. Be6 $143 Rxe6 33. Rxe6 Qc4 $1
34. Qxc4 bxc4 35. Rxf6 Kxa3 36. Rxf7 Re8 $11)) 31. Qxf6 Kxa3 {
Now White wins by force.} (31... Rd1+ $142 32. Kb2 Ra8 (32... Qd4+ 33. Qxd4
