axb4+ Rxb4 (38... Kb6 39. Rxh7 {
and with 3 pawns for the exchange White gradually wins.}) 39. c3 $16 {_|_R}) (
31... Ra8 $2 32. Qb6 a5 33. Ra7 $18) 32. Qxa6+ Kxb4 33. c3+ $1 Kxc3 (33... Kb3
