Nf5 $19) 44... Rb5 45. b3 Kf8 46. Rd7 (46. Rxb7 $2 Bg1+ $19) 46... Ne6 47. Nh4
Ke8 48. Rh7 Nf8 (48... Nf8 49. Rh6 Be3 $1 50. Rh8 Bd4 51. Rh6 Bg7 $19 {
