(7. Qc3 $5 {(Vaganian,R)} f6 8. Nf3 {/\e4+/=/=} (8. Ne4 {Alterman} d6 9. e3 a6
$132)) ({and} 7. Qf3 $5 f6 $140 (7... f5 $2 8. Qc3 Rg8 9. Qxc5 e6 10. Qe3 {
+/=/+/-}) 8. Ne6 $1 Qa5+ (8... dxe6 $2 9. dxe6 Qb6 (9... Bh6 $2 10. Qxa8 $140
