Bh6 $2 10. d6 $16) (9... Na6 10. d6 Rb8 11. Nxf8 Rxf8 12. dxe7 Kxe7 13. Nd2 $14
) 10. Nxf8 Kxf8 11. e4 $14) ({Also badly:} 7. Qxb5 $2 e6 $140 (7... Na6 {
Alterman} 8. Qc4 Bh6 (8... h6 9. Qc3 Rg8 10. Ne4 Bg7 11. Qa3 $14) 9. h4 (9. Ne4
