11. b3 Nb4 12. Qd2 Bb7 13. e4 O-O $44) 8. Ne4 exd5 9. Nxc5 {in view of:} a6 10.
Qb4 $8 Nc6 11. Qa3 d4 $36 (11... Qb6 $2 12. Qe3+ Be7 13. Nd3 Qxe3 (13... d4 $5)
14. fxe3 $14)) 7... Bg7 8. c3 ({Very dangerously:} 8. Qxb5 {because of:} e6 9.
