30. Ne3 Rexf4+ 31. Kg3 Rxf2 32. Nxd5 R8f3+ 33. Kg4 h5+ 34. Kh4 Rxb2 $19) 30...
Rexf4+ 31. Ke3 Rxf2 32. a4 Rg2 $1 {
White has lost two pawns, but his problems are far from over.} (32... bxa4 33.
Ra1 Rxh2 34. Rxa4 Rf6 35. Ra5 $17) 33. axb5 axb5 34. b3 (34. h4 h5 $19) 34...
Rff2 35. Nf3 Rb2 36. b4 Rgc2 37. Kd3 Rf2 38. Ke3 Rbe2+ 39. Kd3 Ra2 40. Ke3
