missing the forceful} 29... Rxd4 $3 30. Qxg4 $1 (30. Rxd4 $2 Bxd4 31. cxd4 (31.
Rxd4 Qxc3 $19) 31... Ne3 $19) (30. cxd4 $2 Ba3 {
with nasty mating threats on the c <->.} 31. Qd2 Nf2 $17) 30... Rxd3 31. Nxd3
