{Excellent defensive move played in cool blood, Morozevich will have a hard
time intensifying his attack.} (19... Bd7 $2 20. Qd3 $18) (19... hxg5 $6 20.
Nxg5 g6 (20... Bd6 21. Qh5) 21. Bxg6 $1 fxg6 22. Nxe6 $16) 20. Ne4 (20. Nxe6 $5
Rexe6 (20... Rdxe6 $2 21. Qd3 $18) 21. Bb3 Rxe3 22. Qxe3 $14) 20... Rdd8 21.
Nfg5 $1 Bd5 $1 22. Qh5 $2 {White got carried away with the prospects of
triumphal attack, this impatient move loses.} (22. Nh7 $1 Bxe4 (22... Kxh7 $2
23. Nf6+ Kh8 24. Rxe8 $18) (22... Be7 23. Nxc5 $1 Bxa2 24. Nf6+ gxf6 25. Qg4+
