An interesting alternative is also to keep the tension with} 6... Ne7 7. Be2
O-O 8. O-O e5 $5 9. a3 f5 10. Ne1 Nd7 11. f3 $6 f4 12. Nd3 h5 13. b4 b6 14. a4
