Bd3 b5 10. Qe2 Bd6 11. a4 b4 12. Ne5 $14 {
1/2-1/2 Shirov,A-Anand,V/Monte Carlo 2001/CBM 81 ext (26)} Bb7 13. Bb5+) 7...
Be7 8. Nxf6+ Bxf6 9. Bxf6 Nxf6 10. Bd3 O-O 11. Qe2 c5 12. O-O-O {
