1/2-1/2 Anand,V-Shirov,A/Monte Carlo 2001/CBM 81 ext (19)}) 8... c5 (8... O-O
$142 $5 {Rabinovich,Al} 9. Bd3 c5 10. Qe2 cxd4 11. Qe4 g6 12. O-O-O e5 13. Bxf6
(13. Qd5 {Rabinovich,Al} Re8 14. Rhe1 Re6 (14... Qe7 {Rabinovich,Al} 15. Bb5
