Rabinovich,Al}) 12. Qb4 $5 {Keeping black king in the center. Black got very
nice position in the game of two unknown players after} (12. O-O-O O-O 13. f4 (
13. Be2 {Rabinovich,Al} e5 $11 {
1-0 Topalov,V-Van Wely,L/Monte Carlo 2001/CBM 81 ext (52)}) 13... Qd5 14. c4
