Bd7 14. Bxd7+ Qxd7 15. O-O-O Nd5 16. Qa3 $36 {
and black still didn't mange to solve opening problems.}) (12... a5 $142 $1 {
Rabinovich,Al} 13. Bb5+ Bd7 14. Qa3 Qe7 $11) 13. Qa3 Qe7 14. Bb5+ Bd7 15. Bxd7+
Kxd7 {Brave decision, but very risky one.   Ftacnik: 'Bareev believes, that he
can solve all his problems with artificial castling idea.'} (15... Qxd7 16.
O-O-O) 16. Qa4+ Kc7 17. Rh3 $1 {White rook joins the party via h3.} a6 18. Rb3
$5 ({Very promising looked} 18. O-O-O $5 $36) 18... Qc5 19. O-O-O b5 $2 {
After this move black is in serious troubles. Deserved attention  Ftacnik:
