Rxb7 Qxf1 27. Rb8+ Kf7 $11) 20... Nf7 $14 (20... Nc6 21. Rd7 Ra7 22. Rf1 Nd4
23. f5 $1 $40)) 20. Rd7 Qe8 21. Rxb7 Nd4 22. Nxd4 cxd4 23. Bd3 {The positions
with ^- are not drawish at all, when heavy pieces are also on the board.} a5
24. Kb1 Rc8 25. Rc1 Rxc1+ 26. Kxc1 e5 (26... Qc8+ 27. Kd1 (27. Kb1 Rg6 28. Rxe7
Rxg3 $44) 27... Rg6 28. Rxe7 Rxg3 29. Ra7 $18) 27. fxe5 Qc6+ 28. Kd1 Qxe4 29.
Bxe4 $18 {The _|_ ^- with rooks gives excellent winning chances, while the _|_
^- is very drawish, and also the R _|_ is very difficult.} g5 30. Rb8+ Kg7 31.
hxg5 Bxg5 32. Bd5 Rg6 33. Rb7+ Kf8 (33... Kh6 $2 34. Be4 $18 {wins outright})
34. Bf7 (34. Rf7+ Ke8 35. Rh7 Rh6 36. Rg7 Be7 37. Kc2 $18 {
was simple and effective.}) 34... Rg7 35. e6 h4 36. gxh4 Bxh4 37. Rb8+ Ke7 38.
Rb5 d3 39. Kd2 Rg3 40. Rxa5 Kd6 (40... Bg5+ 41. Rxg5 Rxg5 42. Kxd3 $18) 41. b4
Bg5+ 42. Rxg5 Rxg5 43. Kxd3 Rg3+ 44. Kc2 $2 (44. Kc4 $1 {was still winning.}
Ra3 45. Kb5 Rxa2 46. e7 $18) 44... Ra3 45. Kb2 Re3 {
and the white K is cut off the third rank.} 46. a4 Kc7 47. Kc2 Kd6 48. a5 Rg3
49. Kb2 (49. b5 Ra3 50. a6 Ra5 51. Kb3 Rxb5+ 52. Ka4 Rb1 53. Ka5 Ra1+ 54. Kb6
Rb1+ 55. Ka7 Rb4 56. Ka8 Rb5 $11) 49... Re3 50. a6 Kc7 51. b5 Kb6 52. Kc2 Re5
53. Kd3 Rxb5 54. Kd4 Kxa6 55. e7 Rb8 56. Kc5 Rc8+ 57. Kd6 Kb6 1/2-1/2

