Bxb5+ axb5 22. Rxc1 Rc8+ 23. Kd2 Rxc1 24. Kxc1 $14) 15... O-O-O 16. Rc1 Kb8 {
Here Black's king is located in complete safety.} 17. g3 a5 $1 {Differently
White will finish development: Bg2, Rhd1 or Rc5,Rhc1 and their position will
